nnoremap H ^
vnoremap H ^

nnoremap L $
vnoremap L $

nnoremap K 10k
vnoremap K 10k
nnoremap J 10j
vnoremap J 10j

"Markdown mode:
vnoremap ` c`<C-r>"`<Esc>
vnoremap * c**<C-r>"**<Esc>
vnoremap i c*<C-r>"*<Esc>

"LaTeX mode:
vnoremap lc c\cancel{<C-r>"}<Esc>
vnoremap lu c\underline{<C-r>"}<Esc>
vnoremap lb c\textbf{<C-r>"}<Esc>
vnoremap lC c\underbrace{<C-r>"}_{}<Esc>i

"Markdown callouts: 
nnoremap cd 0vf]d$
nnoremap ci 0i><Space>[!important]<Space><Esc>$
